  "original_title": "\u0db1\u0dd4\u0d9c\u0dda\u0d9c\u0ddc\u0da9\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dca \u0d86\u0dbb\u0db8\u0dca\u0db7 \u0dc0\u0db1 \u0db6\u0dc3\u0dca \u0db0\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0db1\u0dba\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca \u0d89\u0dc0\u0dad\u0da7",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Away from the bus route starting from Nugegodi",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The private buses starting their journey from Nugegoda bus station started a strike from today (26) demanding that enough diesel be provided to run the buses.",
        "Accordingly, all the buses plying under route numbers 168, 119, 117, 176, 183, 259, 689 starting from Nugegode were withdrawn from service.",
        "Also, the General Secretary of the All Ceylon Private Bus Companies Federation Mr. Anjana Priyanjith said that due to lack of fuel and not getting enough fuel, buses are out of service on many routes.",
        "He also mentioned that although fuel is provided by Langama depot for private buses, it is not enough to run the buses.",
        "He further said that if steps are not taken to provide sufficient fuel, all private buses will be withdrawn from this week."
      ],
